.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-BOTH-RESERVES-SUM" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-both-reserves-sum \- FEAT-2872 channel-both-reserves-sum
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-both-reserves-sum
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sum of (our_reserve + their_reserve) across all peer channels (FEAT-2872).
.PP
Queries all peer channels via lightning-cli listpeerchannels and sums both
our_reserve_msat and their_reserve_msat for every channel.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
